    <briefdescription>
<para>NUMA-aware policy snapshot used by subsystems at runtime. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This policy layer does not perform allocation or placement by itself. It only captures:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>detected sockets (from topology when available),</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>detected NUMA nodes (sysfs-based),</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>env-driven knobs to enable NUMA behaviors,</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>decisions about whether to replicate &quot;hot&quot; blobs. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
